creator: Joy Calls Group, LLC
descriptionHtml:
"Sticks & Skates" is made for amateur ice hockey teams. The app gathers all the necessary information which covers games and training schedule, polls, and team member notifications.

Admins do not require any more to look through all the messages in common groups and chats or chase the player to form a roster for the next game, collect the money or notify about schedule changes or ask for players’ opinions.

Players don’t need any more to chase admins to find out the schedule, roster and confirm their attendance.

All team members get notifications about update changes and are well-informed on all the necessary information by simply checking the app.
descriptionShort: Common team space for managing amateur ice hockey team

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New registration wizard
- Added information about app features
- More convenient invites
